com.activityscheduler.domain

Class Team

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.activityscheduler.domain.AbstractDomainObject
      • com.activityscheduler.domain.Team
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class Team
extends AbstractDomainObject
    A domain object extending AbstractDomainObject to hold the event specific information This class consist of following domain driven design method
    • addScheduledActivities() - Merge all the scheduled input activities to the team catalog
    • addActivity() - Add the input activity to the team catalog
    • getNextActivityStartTime() - Get the Start time of the next activity of the team considering the end time of the existing activity
    Author:
    rbutti
